# Level 3 - Task 1: Predictive Modeling (Classification)

## Project Overview
This project focuses on customer churn prediction using supervised machine learning models. Multiple classification algorithms were trained, evaluated, and compared to determine the best-performing model.

## Objectives
- Preprocess the dataset
- Handle categorical variables
- Scale features
- Train multiple classification models
- Evaluate model performance
- Perform hyperparameter tuning using GridSearchCV

## Dataset
Churn BigML 80 Dataset

## Models Used
- Logistic Regression
- Decision Tree Classifier
- Random Forest Classifier

## Evaluation Metrics
- Accuracy
- Precision
- Recall
- F1-score

## Best Model
Random Forest achieved the best performance with approximately 95% accuracy.

## Tools & Libraries
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Scikit-learn

